Ghost Archive Database
Welcome to the Ghost Archive Database! This database is designed to organize 
and store information related to individuals, families, articles, organizations, 
locations, and investigative cases. It's a versatile structure aimed at 
supporting journalistic investigations.

Table of Contents
Prerequisites
Getting Started
Tables Overview
Populating the Database
Queries and Use Cases
Contributing
